.. option:: --url <url>

   The git URL leading to the repository which is to be exposed;
   Should follow the 'http[s]://host.xz[:port]/path/to/repo.git' format.

.. option:: --username <username>

    The git username used for authorization purposes. Paired with the
    personal token (passed as the --password parameter) can be used to skip
    the default authorization via the command line
    
.. option:: --password <password>

    The git password/personal token.
